String.string: <font size='25'color='#FFCD12'>Is everyone ready?</font></font>
<font size='25'color='#FFCD12'>Which way should I go?</font></font>
<font size='25'color='#FFCD12'>Okay. Syona and I will go this way.</font></font>
<font size='25'color='#FFCD12'>Someone needs to keep Randun out of trouble. I'll go.</font></font>
<font size='25'color='#FFCD12'>Randun, be careful! Don't touch anything!</font></font>
<font size='25'color='#FFCD12'>Nemato? What are you doing?</font></font>
Princess Syona! Don't wander off by yourself!
Then I suppose I'll go with Randun.
Well done. Then, I'll accompany Princess Syona!
What should I do?
Can we just go straight to the Fountain that Seren prophesied?
Well, if we don't succeed, we'll probably find ourselves trapped behind the Storm Barrier.
Look! Over there! There's a light!
We don't know exactly where it is... but there's supposed to be a map with the Fountain marked on it, hidden somewhere in the castle.
We just have to make sure they don't get the Storm Barrier up before we leave, then.
Quiet...there's someone in there.
Did everyone else see that? Those were devans...
Randun! Find someplace safe and stay there!
I'm going this way.
The Guidance Room?
Is this...is this the work of Blood Magic?
You go on ahead. I want to get a closer look at this. Nemato and I will catch up with you shortly.
More Blood Magic...
Nemato! Show us the way out! I'm going to grab a few samples here...
We can't let that happen. Stay here!
The devans...?
They're almost here...? We should go.
If we can not find the Fountain this time.. What is going to happen?
Where would you go? How do we get out of here?
Look at your map!
We don't have time for this. The Fountain is drying up as we speak!
Whoa... did you feel that? Something big is coming!
Where does this door go?
New weapons? I'd like to see those.
A new weapon! A new weapon! This way!
I don't want to get involved, but what can you do?
Oh, thank you! Thank you!
Please... release me!
Greandale is coming! Let me out! Please!
You're here for the Fountain? I can lead you to it!
I'll take you wherever you want to go! Just please let me out!
I think I saw the map you're looking for...in Anea's chamber.
I can take you there!
I remember it distinctly!
We can go this way!
That way is the barracks. Lots of soldiers and new weapons and stuff. It's safer this way.
No...please. If I go that way, they'll kill me for sure!
Thank you, Princess! This way...
Yuk! Don't you feel nauseous? This is where we're staying. Be careful... It's a mess.
They'd just slow me down...
Me? I meant us. They'd slow us down.
Thank you. Heh... maybe things will go better this time...
These used to be my friends...
The slave-soldiers choose who lives... and who goes to the Guidance Room.
It's where Anea conducts her sacred ceremonies...with blood.
Heh... just leave them. They're too scared to even try to escape.
You can count on Nemato!
Through here!
You can find the secret door at the top of the stairs... It will lead you to Anea's palace.
There's a secret passage. I've used it before... heh...
Princess Syona seems very curious about Blood Magic...
You go ahead up the stairs. Look for a lever. I'll go back and watch over Princess Syona...heh...
Food! FOOD!
Intruders! Intruders! Slay them!
Defeat Greandale before the cage is destroyed!
No! No! Let me out!
The cage was destroyed! Your quest has failed. You can try again in a moment.
We're all doomed!
I'm going to die!
We've failed our quest. The event will begin again in a moment.
<font size='30'color='#FF0000'>So tragic... my poor spiders!</font></font>
<font size='30'color='#FF0000'>I see more extreme measures are necessary!</font></font>
Lakan... why have you forsaken me?
Have you met my entourage?
Leave no flesh on their bones!
Ugh... more vermin!
I'll burn you alive!
Nemato went this way.
We shouldn't have trusted him, I guess.
It's locked! Can you break it open?
There's no map here. Nemato lied to us.
I guess Nemato got out through there.
I'd like to investigate that weapon some more...
This way!
I guess it wasn't a total lie.
He was only using us... he won't be any help to us at all...
We're running out of time! We need to find the Fountain.
Randun, no! We've wasted enough time already!
Alright, let's go!
Nemato, you... worm! Princess Syona treated you kindly!
That window is broken...
This glass was broken recently. We might catch him, if we hurry!
More soldiers are probably on the way right now. Let's move!
Hey! Up here...use the elevator...
There are archdevan archers everywhere. They'll spot us if we try to sneak by...
I'll go first. Follow me, but carefully... and don't let those archers spot you!
Wow! This thing is a work of art! Full-compression coils... and it's even got a corrosion-resistant coating!
I guess they've had a lot of time to perfect their processes here...
It's just... beautiful!
This button seems like a design flaw, though...
Intruder alert! Intruder alert! Stop. The. Humanoids!
Oh. Uh... oops?
Sorry about that. Look, you go on ahead. I'll be right behind you!
Masuki! Give me strength!
Here is your chance to prove your love! Do not disappoint me!
Ugh... the pain! Sheer pleasure! It's... invigorating!
A little more! Just a little more! Oh, yes!
Masuki! Don't stop now!
Oh, Sadikin... you were fun while you lasted! But look at these new toys!
No...! Please! Let me serve you a little longer!
This is the last pleasure you will ever feel! Savor it!
You broke my toy! Now I'll have to play...with you.
You will learn to call me Master... and love me for hurting you.
Masuki quickly becomes weak.
Masuki is unbeatable, here. Aim for moments when he's weak.
Sadikin! It's dangerous. Are you okay?
Weakling... you won't beat me!
Please, Masuki! I just need one more chance!
Sadikin... you're enjoying this? Pathetic creature...
Sadikin! I don't think you're going to make it...
Greandale's Cage[?]
There is something on the ground inside the cage.
Blood Magic at Work[?]
Investigate the rotting corpse on the crate.
A Goblin Betrayed[?]
Rescue the goblin peddler from the archdevan soldiers.
The Suspicious Goblin[?]
Find out what the Goblin is hiding.
Completed an additional quest.
Quest Complete!
Thanks! Grrr...
Cheating archdevans! They took all my stock!
You scratch my back... I'll scratch yours!
You helped me, so I'll tell you Anea's secret!
The soldiers talk too much. Anea gets her power from some kind of crystal shard.
This info is worth thousands of gold! But you saved me, so we'll call it even!
Anyway, this Baidun guy said he found something good... Where did he go?
That goblin peddler needs help...
Happy? Can I go now?
